Detailed Description

Columns of Attendees.

Each row of this table represents a single attendee or guest of an event. Both apps and sync adapters may write to this table. There are six writable fields and all of them except ATTENDEE_NAME must be included when inserting a new attendee. They are:

  • EVENT_ID
  • ATTENDEE_NAME
  • ATTENDEE_EMAIL
  • ATTENDEE_RELATIONSHIP
  • ATTENDEE_TYPE
  • ATTENDEE_STATUS
